            "title": "邁亞密網賽｜祖高域獲美斯入場打氣 直言有啲緊張 殺入決賽劍指第100冠",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"祖高域獲美斯入場打氣。Getty/祖高域IG圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/85b00e1b6adf6e9695d7081bd03e31d2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032911131031632.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">祖高域獲美斯入場打氣。Getty/祖高域IG圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>網球名將祖高域於周五邁亞密網賽男單四強直落兩盤擊敗迪米杜夫，殺入決賽距離贏得職業生涯第100冠只差一步。正效力國際邁亞密的球星美斯今仗入場為祖高域打氣，賽後更在更衣室見面，祖高域賽後直言感榮幸之餘也感緊張。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"美斯與祖高域。祖高域IG圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cefc5c0a3412612e1205ca2a78823ec/2025-03/Snapins_ai_486945824_18503748946030927_1150388883579784653_n_1080.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美斯與祖高域。祖高域IG圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"美斯與祖高域。祖高域IG圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af2b892bbee8bb9110fe634ea6f952af/2025-03/Snapins_ai_487087734_18503748955030927_5708318814548707364_n_1080.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美斯與祖高域。祖高域IG圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e8f84c0ae963a41295fbb0a2fbd8bf63/2025-03/GettyImages-2207398234.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d8345e83c03cae2063114b75ed5fbde/2025-03/GettyImages-2207400188.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/464231aa5cafd8308b90cfe45119bb81/2025-03/GettyImages-2207400189.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aaf10c002e1bd68b31fb3f53df0ba9c8/2025-03/GettyImages-2207395875.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/009d6bee070b6b38d4ce55f3ae8537c4/2025-03/GettyImages-2207398235.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入決賽。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"迪米杜夫不敵祖高域。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7cd12b9cc090f98fada989db364689a2/2025-03/GettyImages-2207396160.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        迪米杜夫不敵祖高域。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>祖高域入決賽爭第100冠</h2>\n<p>塞爾維亞名將祖高域今場面對14號種子迪米杜夫打得輕鬆，全場只花69分鐘就以6:2和6:3，直落兩盤取勝殺入決賽。如果他最終封王，將贏得職業生涯第100個錦標，而他的對手將是世界排名54位的非種子的捷克球手文錫克，故奪冠機會高唱入雲。\n\n</p><h2>美斯入場打氣</h2>\n<p>最特別的是，阿根廷球王美斯今仗攜同妻兒入場做觀眾為祖高域打氣，並於賽後到更衣室會面同時交換簽名波衫。祖高域賽後喜言：「看到球王美斯在看台上是我莫大的榮幸。我想這是我第一次在他面前比賽，老實說，我有點緊張。非常感謝他和他的家人一起到場，在他的職業生涯中，我一直都是他的粉絲。我們在更衣室見面並交換了禮物，這是巨大的榮幸，因為他不僅是一名足球員，還是一位偉大的運動員，過去20年在體育界都很有影響力。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060898/即時-體育-邁亞密網賽-祖高域獲美斯入場打氣-直言有啲緊張-殺入決賽劍指第100冠",
