            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "南韓數地山火復燃 傷亡人數升至70人",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"南韓慶尚北道山火焚燒逾一星期仍未救熄。美聯社 　　\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/871b73c91226fb080cb24829051a2050/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032911460278216.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">南韓慶尚北道山火焚燒逾一星期仍未救熄。美聯社 　　</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>南韓慶尚北道山火周五下午被基本撲滅後，當晚義城郡、安東市等地山火再次蔓延。目前，山火導致的總傷亡人數已升至70人，近3000房屋受損，超過6800人流離失所，焚燒面積已超過4.8萬公頃。 \n\n</p>\n<p>今次南韓多地山火已持續超過一星期，成為當地歷史上最嚴重的山林大火。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3441885/\">南韓山火增至28死32傷 近3.8萬人撤離 高球場職員死裏逃生</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"山火導致的總傷亡人數已升至70人。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a2da95cf09471f54b6746ce116bd206/2025-03/V2_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        山火導致的總傷亡人數已升至70人。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"山火已燒毀近3000房屋。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/84f96794c902a1eb08589a8af303b24b/2025-03/V3_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        山火已燒毀近3000房屋。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今次南韓多地山火已持續超過一星期。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5e9dee99eb9f3edd9d4c0366e6492208/2025-03/V4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今次南韓多地山火已持續超過一星期。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"災民家園盡毀。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d867f45774fb3f0a8ec9941de7e327b5/2025-03/V5_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        災民家園盡毀。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今次山火焚燒面積已超過4.8萬公頃。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae6a9ddc5f8fb0c9e94d7b8dfd4dd133/2025-03/V6_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今次山火焚燒面積已超過4.8萬公頃。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>近3000房屋損毀 逾6800人流離失所</h2>\n<p>據南韓中央災難安全對策本部消息，截至當地時間周六上午6時，山火已導致29人死亡、41人受傷，近3000處房屋住宅受損，受山火影響區域面積達4.8萬公頃。目前仍有6800多人因山火流離失所。 \n\n</p>\n<p>韓聯社報道，當地山林部門正展開滅火作業，安東市投入11架直升機撲滅余火，義城郡又新投入3架直升機和230名工作人員參與滅火。\n\n</p>\n<p>至周六上午，安東市山火火勢已得到控制。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
